word_mean_info__list.difference: vi.醒来,睡醒(up);觉醒,振奋 vt.唤醒,弄醒;使觉醒;使振奋,激发;激起
vi.醒来 vt.唤醒,唤起,激起,使认识到 wake (up) to 认识到,意识到
adj.[用作表语]醒着的 vt.唤醒,觉醒 vi.醒,觉醒,意识到
书面用词，常用于被动态和引申意义。
较正式用词，用主动语态时，强调弄醒别人的努力，用被动语态时，指轻而易举地醒过来。可用于引申意义。
普通常用词，指真正的醒来。即可作及物动词也可作不及物动词。
除表示一般的唤醒外，多作引申用。
正式用词，常指觉醒、警惕的状态，也多用于比喻。

bilingual.source: I was awake at dawn and watched the sunrise.
bilingual.target: 我在黎明时醒着的，并观看了日出。

bilingual.source: I try to stay awake during the long meetings.
bilingual.target: 我尽量在长时间的会议中保持醒着的状态。

bilingual.source: She was still awake when I got home last night.
bilingual.target: 昨晚我回家时，她还醒着的。

bilingual.source: The noise from the street kept me awake all night.
bilingual.target: 街上的噪音让我整晚都醒着的。

bilingual.source: He drank coffee to stay awake while studying for the exam.
bilingual.target: 他喝咖啡以在复习考试时保持醒着的状态。

bilingual.source: Sleepwalkers' eyes are open, but they don't see the same way they do when they're awake.
bilingual.target: 梦游者的眼睛是睁着的，但他们看东西的方式和他们醒着的时候不一样。

bilingual.source: He is the only man awake at that time .
bilingual.target: 他是当时惟一醒着的人。

bilingual.source: Tom was the only boy awake at that time.
bilingual.target: 汤姆是那时醒着的唯一的男孩。

bilingual.source: He was the only one boy awake at that time.
bilingual.target: 他是当时惟一醒着的男孩。

bilingual.source: He was the only person awake at the moment.
bilingual.target: 他是那时惟一醒着的人。

list.abstract: awake，字典释义， 唤醒,使醒过来，The thunder awoke me.
《awake》是2005年6月22日发行的一部专辑，由L’Arc~en~Ciel 彩虹乐队演唱。

yingyinNormal.en: George? George, are you awake?
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，乔治，你睡着了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm awake, right? This is happening?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是梦，对吗？这一切都真实在发生。

yingyinNormal.en: Ok, but you must promise you'll stay awake. We promise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，但是你们必须保证你们会保持清醒。我们保证。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you awake? Of course I'm awake. Assume from now on that I'm always awake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还没睡？我当然还没睡。从今往后我是睡不着啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello Kitty's awake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小甜心醒了。

yingyinNormal.en: Pedro has fallen asleep again. I'm awake. I'm awake. Pedro, don't you wear glasses?
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩德罗又睡着了。我醒了，我醒了。佩德罗，你不是带着眼镜的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Let's stay awake all night and see Father Christmas. George is asleep. I'm going to stay wide awake all night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要睡着，等圣诞老人来。乔治已经睡着了。我不睡，我要整夜张着眼睛。

yingyinNormal.en: George. Let's stay awake all night and see Father Christmas. George is asleep. I'm going to stay wide awake all night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治！我们不要睡着，等圣诞老人来。乔治已经睡着了。我不睡，我要整夜张着眼睛。。

yingyinNormal.en: George is not very good at staying awake, but I am. I am going to stay awake and see the Tooth Fairy. I'm not going to sleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来要让乔治一晚上别睡觉有点困难，但我可以，我不能睡着，我必须要见到牙仙子。我绝对不能睡着。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone is tucked up in their beds. Asleep. Baby Alexander is awake. Peppa and George are awake. What's that noise? It's the vacuum cleaner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都上床睡着了。宝宝亚历山大醒了！佩奇和乔治也醒了。那到底是什么声音啊？那是吸尘器的声音。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone is back in their beds. Asleep. Baby Alexander is awake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都回到自己的房间，睡着了！宝宝亚历山大又醒了。

yingyinNormal.en: So is Emma awake yet? No, it's still naptime, but she'll be up soon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，爱玛起来了吗? 没有，现在午睡时间，不过，马上他就会醒了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs. Underwood, President Underwood is on the line. He's awake? Yes, ma'am.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安德伍德夫人，安德伍德总统打来找您。他醒了吗？是的，夫人。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, thank god you're awake. Am I late? Oh, my god. Oh, my god. Did I oversleep?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天哪，你醒了。我睡过头了？是不是？我睡过头了？

yingyinNormal.en: Objection. Come on up. That was a little bit unsubtle. Need to keep the jury awake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 反对。上来吧。刚刚有点咄咄逼人啊。我得让陪审团保持清醒。

yingyinNormal.en: It's that feeling of falling you get that jolts you awake. Snaps you out of the dream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 坠落摇晃直到清醒，瞬间醒梦。

yingyinNormal.en: George, I'm not going to sleep. Let's both stay awake all night and see the Tooth Fairy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，我不打算睡觉了。 今天晚上，我们不能睡着，我们一起来等牙仙子。

yingyinNormal.en: Brutal, isn't it? Here you are, finally awake, and your only wish is to go back to sleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很残忍，不是吗？现在好了，你终于觉醒了，而你唯一的念想就是继续沉睡。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. That was a good idea. About scaring Riley awake. You're not so bad. Really? Nice work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，那是个很好的主意。把莱莉吓醒。你也不是那么坏，真的吗？干得好。

yingyinNormal.en: George's awake. Dinosaur. George, you naughty piggy. Go back to sleep. George is not sleepy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治醒了。恐龙，嘿。乔治，你这淘气的家伙，快闭上眼睛安静睡觉！可是乔治一点也不困。
